			<div class="content" id="post-content-4120292">
									

<p>Coldpost. Potentially a bad idea because this is potentially boring as shit. But I had a lot of Feelings to get out.</p>
<p>Edit to elaborate:</p>
<p>For in-universe reasons I thought this should exist: Read what the Committee has to say. For out-of-universe reasons I thought this should exist: 1) I'm exhausted by the evil portrayal of the Foundation; 'organization that dehumanizes weird people and takes them away' has been done to death in sci-fi and primarily superhero fiction, and there's nothing interesting to come from the relationship between the parties if all that happens between them is textbook mistreatment</p>

							</div>

								
