														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4120306">
									

<p><em>&quot;They may be bound to a contract they have no legal right to opt out of, <strong>common with <a href="/dread-circuses-hub">Herman Fuller's Circus of the Disquieting</a> and <a href="/all-that-glisters">Marshall, Carter &amp; Dark</a></strong>.&quot;</em></p>
<p>Lies! Lies and slander! How dare you impugn the reputation of these honest, respectable businesses which I obviously have no bias towards. Who in their right mind would choose to rot in a Foundation cell when they could tour the Worlds and perform with The Circus of the Disquieting, or hobnob with the <em>creme de la creme</em> in obscene luxury at Marshall, Carter and Dark? Not me good sir. Not me.</p>

