<p>I don't care if the foundation went public in this universe, but containment teams and researchers would never give two shits about what a skips preferred pronouns and names are.<br />
I'm starting to dislike this whole push for a progressive, diverse Foundation.<br />
They are scientists and security officers, they have a job a that's protecting the human race from threats. The skip Is a it and/or object.<br />
